    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold with transparency regarding its current state. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small dents on the passenger side, and some fading in the clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and a few minor stains, though all electronics and controls remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in peak operating condition. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable vehicle at a lower price point who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections.",
