    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously won't believe how gorgeous this ride is. It's been pampered since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014honestly, not a scratch or a speck of dust in sight! It drives like an absolute dream and I've taken such good care of it. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, this is your lucky day! Come take a look, you're going to fall in love! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
