    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, featuring the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. This example maintains its factory-spec vacuum line routing and original apex seal integrity, delivering linear power through a crisp 5-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, supported by the original aluminum double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential. Finished in its original Montego Blue Mica with an immaculate tan leather interior, this FD exhibits zero evidence of heat-cycling fatigue or structural oxidation. A rare opportunity for the purist to acquire a legendary 50:50 balanced platform in a true 'time capsule' state.",
